<chapter xmlns   ="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
         xmlns:xl="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
         xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
         xml:id  ="api-schemas"
         xml:lang="en"
         version ="5.0">
  <title>Endpoint /Schemas</title>
  <para>
    The <literal>/Schemas</literal> endpoint can be used for <literal>GET</literal> method to retrieve supported SCIM schema. The schema provided consists of two parts:
    <itemizedlist mark='bullet'>
      <listitem>
        <emphasis role="strong">Standard Oracle Identity Governance schema</emphasis>, described at https://docs.oracle.com/cd/E52734_01/oim/OMDEV/scim.htm,
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <emphasis role="strong">Custom SCIM schema extension</emphasis>, described throughout this document.
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
    
    The <literal>/Schemas</literal> endpoint is read only.
  </para>
  <para>
    The following API operations are supported by the IGS SCIM Extension <literal>/Schemas</literal> endpoint implementation:
    <itemizedlist mark='bullet'>
      <listitem>
        <link linkend='api-schemas-list'>List SCIM Schemas</link>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </para>
  <xi:include href="list.xml"/>
</chapter>